    "• A novel dataset for analytic essay scoring in German.",
    "Feedback is arguably one of the most important components of educational instruction.",
    "Especially weaker students can profit from highly informative, constructive feedback.",
    "It is meant to help students reach a desired goal by pointing out the discrepancies between their current state and the goal (Hattie & Timperley, 2007; Nicol & Macfarlane-Dick, 2006).",
    "Hattie and Timperly (2007) distinguish four different levels of feedback:"
